Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直都喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直都喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}定是…从我们初遇起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜欢上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是那啥吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}结果是白日梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那句话昨天也说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在这种地方睡觉也会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我做了一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和学姐成为恋人的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是现实哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总觉得还让人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多亏了谷川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}让我注意到了自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川 身体还不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好严重…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还肿着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个样子怎么去见大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没什么好在意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又没变多少…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起这个 你和大家说了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总之说是得了热感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 还算妥当
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了 谁叫我是你的青梅竹马呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呐 前天的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我谁都没说 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 快到吃午饭的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲郎吃完再走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲郎说有事马上就要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜欢海人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜欢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}现在…那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是叫北原同学吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然是同一个小学的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是一个班还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫谷川柑菜 往后请多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又在一个班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全没什么改善
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是我要说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 这是石垣哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请多关照 北原美樱同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的…名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 认识么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊不 女生的名字和长相我全都记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}该说你勤快呢还是说你傻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就不能解释为我是女权绅士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可是花了很长时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多余的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从那之后 已经三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要去哪里么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去探望柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还是别去为好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}现在那家伙的眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊不 感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}眼感？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说是不想把感冒传染给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}连我也不让去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你去了柑菜那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为是青梅竹马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正探望的蛋糕也不能浪费掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 不过是粗茶淡饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想整理一下胶片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐拍了很多回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}挤了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事就不可以?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倒不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我啊 好像喜欢靠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人不喜欢这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也…不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请别在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就那样继续
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}当然在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果真在一起了 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已经做…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 你突然说了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打着拍摄的幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了呢 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雾岛同学 这是我给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定要好好珍惜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这如同奇蹟的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 吃饱了吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然美樱的蛋糕很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也就这点优点了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有优点就很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲郎也有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身材高挑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}相貌堂堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}手又灵巧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很擅长记女孩子的长相和名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那些算不上优点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可以问你一件不好问的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么要邀请贵月学姐参与电影制作？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为海他 貌似想要我这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是没想到学姐会答应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你和她处得那么近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}连我都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你不可能不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么要邀请贵月学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是学姐和雾岛同学变得亲密的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都说了不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是想着要支持海 才向学姐搭话的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在想如果柑菜能参与电影制作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就能缩短与海间的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然不知道这会变成什么结果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是打算两边都支持的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那样的话 哲朗你的心意该何去何从？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你对柑菜的心意又该何去何从？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你那什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一直看在眼里 所以我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗的眼里一直都只有柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么要对自己说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再继续那样逃避下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}时间也不会帮你解决问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}“有什么想说的就说出来吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对我说这番话的不是哲朗你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我才鼓起了勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然那时候说了不用回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但现在能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美樱 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对你…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是我…现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我会和往常一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和大家一起开开心心的拍电影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍好了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在校园文化节之类上放…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我会做回平常那个谷川柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川她今天来我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜欢你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜欢海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜欢海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底该怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我到底 能做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等喝点水后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.02,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在日本泡澡完后习惯要补充水分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一起去散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对了 难得一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就在想晚上也会很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…而且这也是我们的回忆之地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有这么多的自然景观被保留了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好奇怪啊 明明是第一次来的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}却有种让人怀念的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}重新问一下 能不能让我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也帮忙去寻找那个“地方”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我 也想为学姐尽一份力…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}确实 我是以那为目的而来到这个星球的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倒不如说 是想以这次旅行为契机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}并不是因为有什么事发生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才想要做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是 想用这个开始一段什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看看自己能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们都一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那样的话 我就更加想要实现学姐的愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}现在 我只想和海人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想和海人 和大家 一起拍电影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就是我现在的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我早已明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在这个世界上不存在永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为是外星人所以不行是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为不能一直呆在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以无法回应海人的心意是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就打算用着这样的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直从海人身边逃开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为海人得以如愿以偿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那样就…够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我说 你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回来之后 就一直沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找姐姐我商量商量？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我先说了 你就这点不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}保持沉默可不能解决问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}光耍帅是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看似活得无懈可击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但在我看来不过是个小屁孩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跑回娘家的人别那么自豪的谈论人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是回娘家 是离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是说 我还有地方可以回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}夫妻吵架也是有很多种类的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 没和女生交往过的你是不会懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这里有一股处男味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那你就快回…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}受你关照了哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总之 你加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的~好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我都等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}切 又是这德行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了 海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我打算后天重新开始拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以是可以啦 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐也会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 你难道说已经和学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 关于那个我会在和大家见面时说清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…果然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 柑菜要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 我才更加要说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在…干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样的话明天的拍摄就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没问题 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜 有电话找你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}干什么啊 把我叫来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我姑且也算是大病初愈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没关系吧 肿也消了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好！魔术牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:15:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幼稚园的时候 常听到这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那时候明明是我比较高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是什么时候就差了这么多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}以前我被欺负的时候还老给你救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜飞拳是无敌的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很帅气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么啊 讲的这么恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对了 你不是为了讲这些小时候的事才叫我出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说回来你的脚怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有…有些事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那要紧话是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果是海人的事 那就不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我多少知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果没别的事我就回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我觉得你和海要是能顺利就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我却不想看到这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想啊 如果海和学姐能顺利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就能恢复自由什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我做着这样无谓的期待啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明不会有…这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}随意捉弄着自己喜欢的女孩…甚至最后还惹哭她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}却什么也做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜欢的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}骗…骗人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从什么时候起？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的…在我脑袋乱糟糟的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然说些什么呢！笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是 时机选的很差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…终于说出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白的 你喜欢海的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}即便海喜欢一夏学姐 也依然如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就是喜欢这样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就自己把想说的话都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一副自我满足的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别忍耐 柑菜保持柑菜的原样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…不要随便摸女孩子的头发！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要我说你也明白的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哭出来也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不会哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说啊 你来这里犯规了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女孩子可是不屈不挠的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果有了喜欢的人 会变得坚强的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我多亏了哲朗 变了好多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…至少我变得想要去改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想要变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}变得有了这些想望…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这话该由我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感冒已经好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要吃…西瓜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从很久之前就喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜欢学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你 愿意听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}电影 要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倘若世事无常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吾心依旧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摄影机OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这边也好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第275个景
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起 黑衣人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(720,666)}Black man
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我还想呆在这个星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为这星球上有对我很重要的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐说 今天直到傍晚都要好好拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还要拍多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.03,0:23:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我觉得在暑假内能拍完的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还有一周吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你还活着啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你知道我有多担心你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐…姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐为什么到地球来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是那个啦 肯定是来祝福我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊呀讨厌 姐姐真性急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是这样么
